    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740980/extras/e3e825034d30fa890ebf45332548fe04.avif?t=1733936454\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>这只可能是一个发生在蛊婆本体剧情之外的平行世界中的故事。没有姐姐和外公的救援，13岁的阿月拼死也要独自闯出一条生路。没有武器，你能怎么办？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740980/extras/a7522ecad2c79295f3bf2f9c5d10266b.poster.avif?t=1733936454\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740980/extras/a7522ecad2c79295f3bf2f9c5d10266b.webm?t=1733936454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740980/extras/a7522ecad2c79295f3bf2f9c5d10266b.mp4?t=1733936454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>13岁的阿月内心纯净明亮，在她的眼中，姐姐久寻当上蛊婆的那一天将是自己一生中最快乐的时光。然而，突如其来的巨型虫腿瞬间将她捕获，当她再次睁开双眼，居然身处一个冰冷的实验室中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740980/extras/4f7d3630ad2f15cb56b9dcec3f79a009.poster.avif?t=1733936454\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740980/extras/4f7d3630ad2f15cb56b9dcec3f79a009.webm?t=1733936454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>如果……久月在阿姐到来之前……<br>这个混乱的、已经遍布失魄者的实验室突然失控，也许阿月就有机会逃出生天！虽然没有武器，但是从小在丛林中练就的灵活身法，以及阿公教过得草药知识就是她最大的优势。纵然恐惧让她浑身战栗，但这可能真的是最后的机会了！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740980/extras/16d77005ac5f1be3e52dbdc76bae483d.poster.avif?t=1733936454\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1740980/extras/16d77005ac5f1be3e52dbdc76bae483d.webm?t=1733936454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>阿姐！阿公！救我！！！",
